      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLACK STAR RIOT (1) looks overdue for a win having finished in the minors at his last three runs, the latest when third (29.94) at this track. Boasts an unbeaten record from this box. Has the inside draw and looks tough to beat. ON THE PROWL (3) was popular in betting last start but disappointed when 8 lengths away in seventh (30.58). Was in the money the start prior. The form out of last run is most impressive. Great chance to atone. ALGEBRA (2) has good early dash but last time was shuffled out the back and missed the frame, finishing seventh (26.11) in a Grade 5 at Geelong. Fast away and won (26.11) at Geelong the start prior. Is yet to taste defeat at this distance. Must be included in calculations. CONCEIVABLE (7) missed the frame latest (30.26) when eighth over 515m at this track in a R/A FIN. Already a winner from this draw.",
